root: ^Nathan: You are back! I see you scheming that a green little thing there. What's up.

c-0: ^You: Kermit finds you so attractive, capable, macho. He likes you very much and would love to know more about you.
c-1: ^You: Kermit finds you so attractive, capable, macho. He wants to have a date, right now.
g-0: ^Nathan: I am flattered, but between you and me... (quitely) isn't he kinds of too...

s: ^Kermit is risking his family, he is serious!

c-0: ^You: You should talk to Kermit more, he is soft and squishy in a good way!
^Nathan: I just worry about us not having anything in common.
c-1: ^You: Kermit is putting himself out there for you. You should recipricate with at least one date!
^Nathan: What? Wait, then so would I, if I start seeing him.

c-0: ^You: It'll be great for you, I am sure, you both want something different from your lives right now.
c-1: ^You: I am sure you have seen crazier stuff, don't let pesky details misguide you.
^Nathan: Well I could consider this a side-adventure. That would work!
